Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:15.28,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's with that face, Shihoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.78,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.73,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:43.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.35,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Kuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.24,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,What are they going to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.72,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What do you mean? They're going to build a wall, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:06.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Tokyo is crowded as it is. They're just making life more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.32,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Whatever we did, we blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:16.51,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They ditched this place before we were ready to raid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:21.38,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,What do you think about the rumor saying they were affiliated with the terrorists in South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.40,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Who knows? That's the reason we came here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:28.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.38,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.86,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,A hag, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Do you think she's related to this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.74,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:45.04,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll take it with me and report it to my superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.74,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,"Don't bring useless stuff", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.92,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.34,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,They didn't even make an effort to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.26,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Want to go out for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:07.48,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Well, I told my wife I'd be home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's with that? You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.28,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:16.42,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Kuno-san, why don't you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:20.74,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:23.47,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Please make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.34,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Oh, don't go out of your way for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.46,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,There's nothing fancy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.34,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Geez, don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.58,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You just wanted to show off your pretty wife, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.76,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:44.15,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You could at least make an attempt to deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.10,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,How about you, Kuno-san? It's pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.15,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Do you think any woman would be interested in someone with my looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:59.97,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's not true. You're a charming man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:05.06,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're a wonderful wife who's too good for a man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:08.52,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can handle your share of alcohol, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:12.46,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's probably because of my physical build.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:17.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There are times when I wish I could get as drunk as a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:25.24,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Police work requires a person who won't carelessly get drunk and disclose important details, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.37,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'd feel safer with someone who could handle his booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.89,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.37,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You don't get it, Isozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Unlike you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,your wife knows what she's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.62,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.12,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Do you want another bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,No, I'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.89,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:04:00.38,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you actually get drunk for once, Kuno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.41,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,My body won't let me get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:07.39,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Isn't that good? You're making an honest living, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.33,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're being sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.31,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Was he also like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:21.31,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,My husband... Did Isozaki handle alcohol well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:26.70,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yeah... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.49,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Oh, do you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:33.95,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.44,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Talk about great timing. This must be a sign of Her divine guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:42.38,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,Of course! We've come to tell you about something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:46.47,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,Do you believe in anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.58,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... I don't understand much Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.71,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Nonsense! If you understand that much, it's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.06,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... I need to bring my things inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.38,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Let us hold it for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:00.85,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.41,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.00,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,What an admirable young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.83,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,You actually cook instead of eating pre-packaged food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.74,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... Like I said, I need to put this inside the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.44,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Shall we cook it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.58,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,What were you going to make? A kimchi pot dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.50,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,As a Korean, he probably will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.36,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I never said I was Korean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.36,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Are you from China?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.78,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Ni hao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.81,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Good! Kawakami-san, hand him a pamphlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.30,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,That's right! There happens to be a Chinese edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.26,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.68,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,Isn't she beautiful? She's the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.98,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,You're a lucky one. This was certainly the guidance of Gate-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.95,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Are you interested in Gate-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:47.17,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,Really? You must listen to what we have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:52.11,DTB-Default,Yamashita,0,0,0,,We worship Gate-sama, who is an embodiment of our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:56.62,DTB-Default,Kawakami,0,0,0,,Have you heard about the Fellowship of the Gate Fundamentalists, also known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.67,DTB-Default,Member,0,0,0,,In this world where the moon has vanished and the stars have changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.98,DTB-Default,Member,0,0,0,,we must not be frightened or intimidated. Let us pray instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.30,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The Brotherhood of the Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.43,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's one of those new cults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.01,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's a recent fad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.93,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.64,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:20.87,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You're to infiltrate the cult and kill the star of Arma, their guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.09,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Those are your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.82,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Fortunately, there'll be an initiation for non-members next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.24,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The woman in the picture is the undercover source.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.95,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You're to work with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:41.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko, you were a part of the syndicate after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.37,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.92,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.74,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't make a scene. If you're going to pick somebody's pocket, choose your targets wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.63,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm not some pigeon, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:58.88,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:00.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.83,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.97,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I told you I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:22.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.91,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.99,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.85,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I don't really have a choice, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.97,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm sort of responsible for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:39.00,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Sort of? You accused me of being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.17,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's no way I made a mistake about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.59,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I didn't take your wallet, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.48,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.61,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:53.58,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I understand the position you're in. That's why I settled the details of the accident out of court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:58.77,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Besides, I missed my audition because of that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.24,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,You've caused me a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.75,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.36,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It was for a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.60,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:13.06,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I only had a one-in-a-million shot, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:17.97,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Not that I care. When I get released from here, you're going to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.98,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Why are you so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:26.94,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The penalty won't be anything excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.65,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:32.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm surprised by how many changes in expressions you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Does that come from your acting background?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.59,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.68,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,You're no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:52.10,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Why aren't you drunk after drinking that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I told you I can't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:57.30,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That's no fun, Kiyopii!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.18,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:07.87,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Your name's Kiyoshi. What's wrong with calling you Kiyopii?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.84,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Geez, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.61,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going? Your house is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.05,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You crazy drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.00,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's not because I'm drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.05,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,even though I'm pretty buzzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.76,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.27,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's obvious I did it because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't joke around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,How could you like me? You hardly know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.19,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's not an issue about knowing more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.12,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Good things can come out of not knowing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.60,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.83,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's a limit to how much you can hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.19,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Right, Shihoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.61,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Nineteen Dreaming Shallow, Uninebriated... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:28.42,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,When the wild spirit descends upon this land,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:32.85,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,misery of colossal proportions will accompany it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:42.02,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Gate-sama is not the wall built by the efforts of the lecherous,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:46.33,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,but the pristine spirit hidden within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:50.45,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,That ray will light the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:57.09,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The guru makes an appearance before her apostles during an event that only occurs once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.09,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,It'll be difficult to locate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What about the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:06.29,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She's scheduled to instruct the initiates tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.07,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:13.69,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,reporting periodically will be difficult. Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.71,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why do you want to be constantly updated anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.72,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is there something you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.05,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:28.98,DTB-Default,Trainee,0,0,0,,The guru continued to witness the impending misery for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.13,DTB-Default,Trainee,0,0,0,,One day, She had attained enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.53,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:39.24,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,We'll move on to page 201, The Dark Gospel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.43,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.41,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.86,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Please read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.62,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.3\bord0\shad0\fs35\fnSegoe Print\frz348.447\pos(365,650)\c&H273032&}Sanctification Room, 1:00 am
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:51.03,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The Dark Gospel, verse seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:55.93,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The moon was spirited away. On this night, misery descended upon the sacred land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:12:00.34,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The moon disappeared, and the stellar constellation was renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.35,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.33,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Sit down. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.61,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,This room is the equivalent of a confessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.62,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Respect of privacy is the rule of thumb here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.32,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I've already inspected the room anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:24.22,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Underneath the main chamber lies a secret area that only the guru and her trusted apostles know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.75,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,You'll be able to find the entry route with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:31.28,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The guru will be meeting an important person on the day after tomorrow at 2 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.23,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What'll happen at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.73,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'll deal with the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.98,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,However, since I can't use my power repeatedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.67,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,you'll have to take care of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.49,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.90,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It took me three years to get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:47.91,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:52.16,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It was necessary to gain the trust of the cult,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.92,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,as well as identify the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.08,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Identify?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.36,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Does she have a body double?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.02,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Yes, but that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:04.68,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've been informed that the guru is a contractor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.27,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,but were you told about her ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.18,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.56,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Do you remember the incident that occurred six years ago, when a politician named Hirose was assassinated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:17.42,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,He was killed by his female secretary. There were witnesses who saw her in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:22.30,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The politician had connections with the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.85,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,He had taken initial steps in an attempt to disband the cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.92,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What the syndicate learned through a subsequent investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:34.61,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,was that the person who killed him wasn't his secretary, but her look-alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.73,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,They weren't twins, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.21,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The punch line's even worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:44.05,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The murderer transformed into the secretary and murdered Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.46,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That is the ability of Arma the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.72,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.18,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.02,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you closing soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.75,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.73,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm glad you come to visit on his memorial day every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:08.53,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,During the afternoon, a relative of his stopped by and talked about Isozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.93,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Our conversation didn't last very long, and I felt vexed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.11,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me these kinds of things happen frequently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:22.13,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,When a family member is killed, you lose your memory out of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.59,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You said it happened all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:27.68,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yeah, I might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:32.77,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Could that be true? Was I that distant from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.33,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.75,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I even have faint memories of you, Kuno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:44.25,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The man I lived with for two years, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.00,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I don't remember him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.79,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about what you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:56.22,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Some things are better left that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.08,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's okay. I know how to get to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's the third time. I won't get lost this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.70,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,I need to get some fresh air anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.60,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.07,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.05,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.61,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Is she an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.04,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Kuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.90,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.46,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.38,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.66,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Dear! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.72,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Honey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.26,DTB-Default,Isozaki,0,0,0,,Shi... zu... ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:41.83,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.05,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.67,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Wait, Shihoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.41,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:50.79,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.54,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The case was closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.29,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\fay-0.14\fscx80\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&\pos(712,105)\frz139.157}Letter of\N resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Investigations have been concluded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.81,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Due to the abnormal nature of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:08.30,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,it was categorized with the other special cases that have been occurring recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Special cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.03,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.91,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Those with supernatural powers, referred to as contractors, have been at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.56,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:22.33,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,At the gate during the turmoil in South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.29,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,there were stories about the same kinds of people being involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:31.21,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,This is the autopsy report on Isozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.17,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,He died from complications resulting from deterioration of his internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:40.35,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Although we know what took place, we still don't know how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.06,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,We're not prepared to deal with these kinds of cases at this moment in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.88,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,That is all I can tell you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.98,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I don't know why you submitted this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:55.71,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,but this case has been dealt with internally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.03,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to resign. That's what I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:03.40,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko, what exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.01,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Kuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:18.32,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Did you know that it's standard procedure to erase the memories of those who have witnessed a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:22.75,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,You saw her when Isozaki-san was killed, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.79,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,That's why your memories will be erased in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.51,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,There are some people who have voiced regrets about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:35.84,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,citing your proficiency as an intelligence officer who could be of some use to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.55,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:41.76,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Parts of Mrs. Isozaki's memories have already been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.63,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:46.19,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Won't you consider joining the syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:51.50,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,It's the only way you'll be able to prevent the erasure of your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.82,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Oh, my. It's starting to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:24.16,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I would commend you on assembling this many,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.28,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,but it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:28.21,DTB-Default,Officer,0,0,0,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.92,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like you can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.07,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Arma the guru better be available today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.24,DTB-Default,Officer,0,0,0,,She's waiting in another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.20,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I'm drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.66,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That man... He was there with Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.40,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,How are the preparations going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.38,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.77,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,What an unenthusiastic reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.41,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Don't treat dolls like tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.78,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Is this in accordance with Amber's wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.83,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of E.P.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.92,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Kishida, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.39,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It looks like you're able to see observer apparitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.84,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Are you a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.52,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.31,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.57,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.18,DTB-Default,Officer,0,0,0,,Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.61,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Are you the contractor who was sent to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.58,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.92,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Damn, he shouldn't be too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.98,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:12.93,DTB-Default,Officer,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.19,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You blew it? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.36,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Did you order Yin to send an observer apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.12,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was worried about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.70,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you do something like that? That isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:28.01,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The woman... What happened to the undercover agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.73,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She was caught, no thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.20,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Did you hear what I said, Huang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.28,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.54,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A friend who was erased, a memory likewise erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.46,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Thoughts that won't disappear, a woman who disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.27,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Contractors don't have a sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.88,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Their memories simply remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.76,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The muzzle shines a somber color of rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.44,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Putting an end to what was smoldered in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:05.27,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,basking in joy, you wake up from a dream that vanishes as easily as a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.17,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,However, you wanted to get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.34,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Twenty Dreaming Shallow, Uninebriated... (Part Two)